{"tid":686734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★美國青少年正拋棄Facebook　僅10%經常用！","createTime":"2018-06-01T14:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T04:59:48.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6efdc4d8d15217320ef77d84b474e1b8342bfb72","tid":686734,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"外電報道，皮尤研究中心(Pew Research Center)最新公布的調查報告顯示，更多美國青少年(13歲至17歲)正在拋棄Facebook，轉而投向「閱後即焚」通訊應用Snapchat和Alphabet旗下YouTube等競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n調查發現，51%的美國青少年仍在使用Facebook，但與3年前的71%相比已大幅下降。然而，有85%受訪者現正使用YouTube，榮登首位，排在第2位的是Facebook旗下照片共享社交網站Instagram，比例為72%；再其次則是Snapchat，為69%。<br />\n<br />\n調查表明，僅有10%的美國青少年稱，其最常使用Facebook，相比之下YouTube和Snapchat分別為32%和35%。<br />\n<br />\n無論美國青少年偏愛哪個平台，調查發現他們幾乎把所有時間都花在網上。45%受訪者稱，其幾乎不間斷地上網，44%則稱其一天之內會多次上網，僅有11%稱其上網頻率不那麼高。相比之下，皮尤研究中心2014至2015年調查發現，當時僅有24%青少年稱，其幾乎不間斷地上網。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180601/bkn-20180601213426908-0601_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180601%2Fbkn-20180601213426908-0601_00842_001.html&d=iwrpB9Jvb375Ye5ZGadx1NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=7311f573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180601/bkn-20180601213426908-0601_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f727113b2d2c8695ac0da108c44304215f74d06a","tid":686734,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/142556_b14f0a4a6cd1ebbac3e71dfcf1ab98b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F142556_b14f0a4a6cd1ebbac3e71dfcf1ab98b2.png&h=57b4121a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4cc04d2eaf45d389e785e03948f128004042690","tid":686734,"uid":17738,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"冇人理老貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <